	<div class="relative">
		<h1>Comfortable is smart.</h1>
		<h2>Hi-tec fabrics keep you dry, fresh, and clean.</h2>
		
		<!-- insert image here -->
		
		<div class="icons">
			<span class="icon" id="moisture"></span>
			<h3>Hi-tech silver fabric kills stink.</h3>
			<p>The VisaEndurance® line of silver ion fabrics uses 100% pure silver to kill bacteria that causes odor. Made for soldiers. Now brought to you.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="icons">
			<span class="icon" id="silver"></span>
