		<h1>You can't afford to be uncomfortable.</h1>
		<h2>Feel great and have two armbands for the price of one of those cludgy thingamajiggers.</h2>
		
		<!-- insert main background image -->
		
		<div class="icons">
			<span class="icon" id="comfort"></span>
			<h3>Comfortable placement for optimal performance.</h3>	
			<p>Fabrics that wick moisture away from your arm to dry faster. So you and your device stay dry and cool.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="icons">
			<span class="icon" id="touchthrough"></span>
			<h3>Touch-through, see-through fabrics</h3>
