		</div>
		<div class="icons closingicon">
			<span class="icon" id="novelcro"></span>
			<h3>No Velcro. No Plastic.</h3>
			<p>No buckling velcro bands on your upper bicep. No shiney plastic bag screen protectors that retain moisture.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="closingdiv relative">
		<h1>Safety First</h1>
		<h2>Say hello to oncoming traffic.</h2>
		
		<!-- insert image here -->
		
		<div class="icons closingicon">
			<span class="icon" id="safety"></span>
			<h3>Reflectivity Strips</h3>
			<p>Comfe Arms features 3M® retroreflective material to improve safety while on the roads.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="closinglinks">
